title: Are Ranked Queues Disabled?
body: I only have the option to queue for Blind Pick. The only alert is that ZZ'Rot has been disabled. Anyone else unable to queue for ranked?

replies.body: I didn't see any records of ranked being disabled. Are you still experiencing this issue or has it been resolved by now?
same issue. twisted treeline also unavailable.
I've been experiencing the same thing... It started this evening, it was letting me play ranked earlier today :/
